      • treat

        public void treat()
        Treats disease in the current city. Removes one infection level, or all levels if disease has been cured. Diseases with highest infection level at current city are prioritized.

      • discardCards

        public void discardCards​(java.util.TreeMap<java.lang.String,​City> cities,
                         boolean isYcured,
                         boolean isRcured,
                         boolean isBcured,
                         boolean isGcured)
        Discards cards from this pawn's hand. Cards of cured diseases are discarded first. Cards colors of which have the smallest count in this hand are prioritized for discarding.
        Parameters:
        cities - - list of sities on the map
        isYcured - - true of yellow disease has been cured
        isRcured - - true of red disease has been cured
        isBcured - - true of blue disease has been cured
        isGcured - - true of green disease has been cured
